metadata.name: TULPAKIN IKONS #1
metadata.description:
TULPAKIN ICONS consists of a collection of 456 unique individually created autotelic ideograms, which are rendered as visionary techno-fauvist neon-brut cyberpop tulpa portraits.
The series acts as a limited edition PFP project made up of legendary 1/1 art with mystical hand crafted art and super secret rare mystery attributes.
Each inspiring multifaceted work is a piece of fine art, holding rich layers of meaning to unpack and activate through exposure and reflection.
Yet can also be used as a profile picture and act as your digital identity across the metaverse.
Owners of TULPAKIN ICONs become members of the TULPATOWN community and can access exclusive gated art and experiences.
